31#include "gmp.h"
32#include "gmp-impl.h"
33
34
35/* Something like mpq_cmpabs_ui would be more useful for the neg/neg case,
36 and perhaps a version accepting a parameter to reverse the test, to make
37 it a tail call here. */
38
39int
40_mpq_cmp_si (mpq_srcptr q, long n, unsigned long d)
41{
42 /* need canonical sign to get right result */
43 ASSERT (SIZ(DEN(q)) > 0);
44
45 if (n >= 0)
46 return _mpq_cmp_ui (q, n, d);
47 if (SIZ(NUM(q)) >= 0)
48 {
49 return 1; /* >=0 cmp <0 */
50 }
51 else
52 {
53 mpq_t qabs;
54 SIZ(NUM(qabs)) = -SIZ(NUM(q));
55 PTR(NUM(qabs)) = PTR(NUM(q));
56 SIZ(DEN(qabs)) = SIZ(DEN(q));
57 PTR(DEN(qabs)) = PTR(DEN(q));
58
59 return - _mpq_cmp_ui (qabs, NEG_CAST (unsigned long, n), d); /* <0 cmp <0 */
60 }
61}
